<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>サーバーエラー (500)</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <style>
    html, body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Shippori Antique B1', sans-serif;
      background: 
        linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8)), 
        url('<%= asset_pack_path("media/images/main.jpg") %>') no-repeat center center fixed;
      background-size: cover;
      color: #2e6044;
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    main {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-grow: 1;
      padding: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    a {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      background-color: #2e6044;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    a:hover {
      background-color: white;
      color: #2e6044;
      border: 1px solid #2e6044;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <main>
    <h1>サーバー内部でエラーが発生しました</h1>
    <p>一時的な問題の可能性があります。しばらくしてから再度お試しください。</p>
    <a href="/">トップページへ戻る</a>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
